de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.adhoc.model

Interface AHOfferModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHOffer>, com.liferay.portal.model.ClassedModel, Cloneable, Comparable<AHOffer>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AHOffer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AHOfferBaseImpl, AHOfferClp, AHOfferImpl, AHOfferModelImpl, AHOfferWrapper

    public interface AHOfferModel
extends com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHOffer>
    The base model interface for the AHOffer service. Represents a row in the "AHOFFER" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation AHOfferModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in AHOfferImpl.

    Author:
    Brian Wing Shun Chan
    See Also:
    AHOffer, AHOfferImpl, AHOfferModelImpl
